text: Chikman () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Skopkortnenskoye Rural Settlement, Alexandrovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km north- east from Skopkortnaya. == References == Category:Rural localities in Alexandrovsky District
title: Chikman
